---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services - Points Beyond">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Services</h1>
      <p>AI-optimized strategies for the modern search landscape</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/><path d="M11 8v6"/><path d="M8 11h6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)</h2>
          <p class="service-intro">
            The way people find information has fundamentally changed. When someone asks ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude, or Google AI Overview a question about your industry, your content should be the answer they receive.
          </p>
          <p>
            Answer Engine Optimization positions your brand as the authoritative source that AI systems cite when responding to user queries. Unlike traditional SEO which optimizes for link clicks, AEO focuses on becoming the definitive answer—the content AI trusts enough to quote directly.
          </p>
          <h3>What We Deliver</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>AI Citation Strategy</strong> — Structure your content so AI systems recognize and cite it as authoritative</li>
            <li><strong>Question-Answer Optimization</strong> — Format content to directly answer the questions your audience asks AI</li>
            <li><strong>Entity & Knowledge Graph Alignment</strong> — Ensure your brand and offerings are correctly understood by AI systems</li>
            <li><strong>Featured Snippet Targeting</strong> — Capture Google's featured snippets and AI Overview positions</li>
            <li><strong>Competitive AI Visibility Analysis</strong> — Understand where competitors appear in AI responses and how to surpass them</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</h2>
          <p class="service-intro">
            Traditional search isn't going away—it's evolving. Google still processes billions of searches daily, and ranking well remains essential for visibility, credibility, and traffic.
          </p>
          <p>
            We combine proven SEO fundamentals with AI-era strategies to ensure your content performs across both conventional search results and the new AI-curated responses appearing at the top of search pages. Our approach builds sustainable organic visibility that compounds over time.
          </p>
          <h3>What We Deliver</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Technical SEO Audits</strong> — Comprehensive analysis of site architecture, speed, mobile experience, and crawlability</li>
            <li><strong>Keyword Research & Strategy</strong> — Data-driven keyword targeting including AI query pattern analysis</li>
            <li><strong>Content Gap Analysis</strong> — Identify high-value topics your competitors rank for that you're missing</li>
            <li><strong>On-Page Optimization</strong> — Title tags, meta descriptions, headers, and content structure optimization</li>
            <li><strong>Link Building Strategy</strong> — Ethical, sustainable approaches to building domain authority</li>
            <li><strong>Performance Tracking</strong> — Monthly reporting on rankings, traffic, and conversion metrics</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>AI Voice Receptionist</h2>
          <p class="service-intro">
            Never miss a call again. Our AI Voice Receptionist answers your business phone 24/7 with natural, human-like conversation—booking appointments, answering FAQs, and ensuring every caller gets immediate attention.
          </p>
          <p>
            Unlike basic voicemail or rigid phone trees, our AI receptionist handles real conversations. It understands context, manages interruptions, and adapts to each caller's needs. Your customers get instant service while you focus on running your business.
          </p>
          <h3>What We Deliver</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>24/7 Call Answering</strong> — Every call answered instantly, day or night, weekends and holidays</li>
            <li><strong>Appointment Scheduling</strong> — Real-time calendar integration to book, reschedule, and confirm appointments</li>
            <li><strong>FAQ Handling</strong> — Instantly answer questions about hours, services, pricing, location, and policies</li>
            <li><strong>Natural Conversations</strong> — AI that handles interruptions, follow-up questions, and complex requests naturally</li>
            <li><strong>Call Summaries & Transcripts</strong> — Detailed records of every conversation delivered to your inbox</li>
            <li><strong>Custom Voice & Personality</strong> — Tailored to match your brand tone and business requirements</li>
            <li><strong>Seamless Handoff</strong> — Warm transfer to your team when human attention is needed</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <h2>Let's Build Your AI Strategy</h2>
        <p>Every business has unique needs. Let's explore how Points Beyond can help you thrive in the AI era.</p>
        <a href="/points-beyond/contact/" class="cta">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2e8f0 0%, #a78bfa 50%, #8b5cf6 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .services {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .service {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .service-icon {
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .service-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .service-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
  }

  .service-intro {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .service-content ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .service-content li {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.75rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.6;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
  }

  .service-content li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .service-content li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
  }

  .service-content li strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .cta-section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .cta-card {
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .cta-card h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .services {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .service {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .service-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .service-intro {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-card {
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .cta {
      padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
